《'''毕业会考'''》（{{Lang-ro|'''Bacalaureat'''}}；working title：''Family Photos''）是一部2016年[[克里斯蒂安·蒙久|克里斯蒂安·蒙久]]编剧并执导的[[罗马尼亚|罗马尼亚]]电影，[[Adrian_Titieni|Adrian Titieni]]主演。获得[[2016年戛纳电影节|2016年戛纳电影节]]最佳导演奖。<ref name="IW">{{cite web |url=http://www.indiewire.com/article/cannes-live-stream-2016-film-festival-lineup-list |title=2016 Cannes Film Festival Announces Lineup |accessdate=14 April 2016 |work=IndieWire |archive-date=2016-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160520032842/http://www.indiewire.com/article/cannes-live-stream-2016-film-festival-lineup-list |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="VarCannes">{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2016/film/festivals/cannes-film-festival-official-selection-lineup-2016-1201753269/ |title=Cannes 2016: Film Festival Unveils Official Selection Lineup |accessdate=14 April 2016 |work=Variety |archive-date=2016-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160930211716/http://variety.com/2016/film/festivals/cannes-film-festival-official-selection-lineup-2016-1201753269/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ent.btime.com/movie/20160523/n159910.shtml |title=大爆冷！阵容强大的戛纳被眼瞎的评委毁了 |accessdate=2016-05-23 |archive-date=2016-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160602222320/http://ent.btime.com/movie/20160523/n159910.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 剧情 ==
故事发生在罗马尼亚的一个小城镇，主角是一个[[医生|医生]]。讲述他为了让被性侵的女儿顺利[[毕业|毕业]]而不惜一切代价的故事<ref name="fne" />。

