==制作==
据导演[[Cristian_Mungiu|Cristian Mungiu]]表示，故事的灵感来自于他的生活以及为人父母的经历<ref>{{Cite web|last=Goodfellow|first=Melanie|date=2015-03-12|url=http://www.screendaily.com/news/cristian-mungiu-reveals-first-details-of-next-film/5084189.article|title=Cristian Mungiu reveals first details of next film|work=[[Screen_International|Screen International]]|accessdate=2016-04-02|archive-date=2016-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160423170031/http://www.screendaily.com/news/cristian-mungiu-reveals-first-details-of-next-film/5084189.article|dead-url=no}}</ref>。导演的公司 Mobra Films 以及 [[Why_Not_Productions|Why Not Productions]]、[[Wild_Bunch_(company)|Wild Bunch]]、Les Films du Fleuve、[[France_3|France 3]] Cinéma 和 [[Mandragora_Movies|Mandragora Movies]]为出品方。并获得罗马尼亚国家电影中心191万[[罗马尼亚列伊|罗马尼亚列伊]]的资助。2015年6月11日到7月24日在罗马尼亚[[布拉索夫縣|布拉索夫縣]]的小镇[[Victoria,_Brașov|Victoria]]取景拍摄。<ref name="fne">{{Cite web|last=Blaga|first=Iulia|date=2015-08-11|url=http://www.filmneweurope.com/news/romania-news/item/110969-production-cristian-mungiu-wraps-shooting-for-family-photos|title=Production: Cristian Mungiu Wraps Shooting for Family Photos|work=Film New Europe|accessdate=2016-04-02|archive-date=2016-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160405082218/http://www.filmneweurope.com/news/romania-news/item/110969-production-cristian-mungiu-wraps-shooting-for-family-photos|dead-url=no}}</ref>

